, most baseball executives and managers rejected Cook's mathematical approach and academic language.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%227%22])">7</ref> He was also criticized for lax mathematical models and inadequate numerical evidence by statisticians, such as <link>
